{"tid":441899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文革重臨預備]薄熙來、周永康等人「陰謀篡黨奪權」","createTime":"2017-10-20T06:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T12:55:16.000Z","uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93d5ef63a9993b48b2b6a42ce90982621116857b","tid":441899,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:04:53.000Z","msg":"【劉士余：薄熙來、周永康等人「陰謀篡黨奪權」】<br />\n【語出驚人　文字直播立即停止】<br />\n<br />\n中國證監會主席劉士余，在出席中共十九大代表團會議時稱，過去5年，中共粉碎了「篡黨奪權」的陰謀，是習近平在關鍵時候挽救了黨和國家。<br />\n<br />\n劉士余亦特別點名了薄熙來、周永康、令計劃、徐才厚、郭伯雄、孫正才六個落馬官員。不過這些人下台時，官方都是統一口徑：「反貪腐。」劉士余的發言明顯與官方說法不一，而此話一出，中國網就立即終止代表團會議的文字直播。<br />\n<br />\n中共小字典：「篡黨奪權」這個字眼極為嚴厲，可以追溯至毛澤東年代的黨內權鬥，曾用來形容林彪和四人幫。趙紫陽或胡耀邦都沒有受到如此對待。"},{"pid":"f9116ffcf09132cc2fd308654d182bccee291d91","tid":441899,"uid":22310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:47:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qxyYZZDtGN8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqxyYZZDtGN8&d=yxF5I2YAp5zYew9dlCv25JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=b63850c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qxyYZZDtGN8</a><br />\n好好睇"},{"pid":"7714e1c6f77140b2a74fa9711053c0dfb14d350e","tid":441899,"uid":16647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/qxyYZZDtGN8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqxyYZZDtGN8&d=yxF5I2YAp5zYew9dlCv25JUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=b63850c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qxyYZZDtGN8</a><br />\n好好睇</blockquote><br />\n使唔使咁大聲講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7734f5e1b71b120b761a05e767ed546b56be1add","tid":441899,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T12:55:16.000Z","msg":"都搞到人去唔到英國讀書啦重想點呀"}]}